{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"24":{"eng-name":"The Chapters on Jihad","ara-name":"كتاب الجهاد"}},"section_detail":{"24":{"hadithnumber_first":2753,"hadithnumber_last":2881,"arabicnumber_first":2753,"arabicnumber_last":2881}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2833,"arabicnumber":2833,"text":"حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ نُمَيْرٍ، حَدَّثَنَا يُونُسُ بْنُ بُكَيْرٍ، عَنْ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ إِسْحَاقَ، عَنْ يَزِيدَ بْنِ رُومَانَ، عَنْ عُرْوَةَ، عَنْ عَائِشَةَ، أَنَّ النَّبِيَّ صلى الله عليه وسلم قَالَ ‏ \"‏ الْحَرْبُ خُدْعَةٌ ‏\"‏ ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih Mutawatir"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih Mutawatir"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":24,"hadith":81},"chapter":{"id":28,"ara-name":"باب الْخَدِيعَةِ فِي الْحَرْبِ","eng-name":"Deceit in war","isFirstHadith":true}}]}